<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1187</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ men yǒu yī gè xīn yuàn, jiù shì jīn shēng néng bèi nǐ yòng.
 sòng shuǐ gěi jī kě de rén qún, chuán fú yīn gěi měi yī gè rén tīng.
 yǒu nǐ cái yǒu zhēn píng ān, yǒu nǐ cái yǒu zhēn shēng mìng.
 chuān guò suì yuè chūn yǔ qiū, kàn pò chén shì jiē xū kōng.
 qiān guà nà shī sàng de líng hún, tīng jiàn lái zì mǎ qí dùn de hū shēng.
 kū qì wèi tóng bāo dài qiú, shēn yuān jiù yǔ shēn yuān xiǎng yīng.
 yùn yù wú shù kē zhōng guó xīn, jiǔ bǎi liù shí wàn píng fāng gōng lǐ de xīn xiōng,
 wèi jī dū yíng dé xiào yuán, wǒ men yuàn zuò zhǔ de jīng bīng.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a wǒ men yǒu yī gè xīn yuàn 迦南1187</title>
</song>